sentences: The Carrier was an American melodic hardcore band from Boston, Massachusetts, United States, which formed in 2006.
In 2006, the band self-released their debut demo whom they recorded with Jay Maas at the Getaway Group Studios.
After a year of playing shows, in the summer of 2007 the band teamed up with Words of War Records to release a self-titled 7".
